  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 and more

          -  Parkinson's disease according to UKPDSBB diagnosis criteria

          -  Motor difficulties in spite of dopaminergic per os treatment

          -  Not eligible for deep brain stimulation for one or more reasons (age&gt;70, axial
             troubles in spite of dopaminergic per os treatment, cognitive troubles and/or
             hallucinations)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Mattis scale &lt; 120

          -  Contraindication to Apomorphine (liver insufficiency, severe cognitive troubles,
             allergy, pregnancy, neuroleptic treatment)

          -  Contraindication to Fluoro-Deoxy-Glucose which is used in PET-Scan (allergy, kidney
             failure, pregnancy, breast feeding)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
